text: The Military ranks of Luxembourg are the military insignia used by the Luxembourg Army. Luxembourg has neither an air force nor a navy. ==Commissioned Officers== The rank insignia for commissioned officers for the army. {| style="border:1px solid #8888aa; background-color:#f7f8ff; padding:5px; font-size:95%; margin: 0px 12px 12px 0px;" |} Army-LUX-OF- CiC.svg| ==Enlisted== The rank insignia for enlisted personnel for the army. {| style="border:1px solid #8888aa; background-color:#f7f8ff; padding:5px; font-size:95%; margin: 0px 12px 12px 0px;" |} ==Notes== ==References== ==External links== * Armyrecognition Luxembourg Army * Uniforminsignia.org (Luxembourg Army) Category:Military of Luxembourg
